descriptionHtml: This is just something I made for the heck of it. I added a blacksmiths clothes and shoes with a modified enchant for smithing on the clothes and alchemy on the shoes. They fortify your skill by 116%. The percentage gets a bit higher as you level. You can find them in Whiterun on the ground by the Skyforge. If there are any problems with the gear I am sorry I am not a modder of any skill level (incredible noob). Have fun! :)
author: ZGaming
